    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for Route4Me API. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. Route4Me's API reference covers optimization problems, routes, orders, addresses, vehicles, geocoding, tracking, activity feeds, territories, and telematics connections. The public docs show route and order CRUD, route path and tracking-history retrieval, asset-tracking lookups, GPS position submission, live user-location queries, vehicle APIs, and telematics-connection management through the Operational Assessment gateway. That makes the platform useful both for logistics master data and for operational telemetry derived from tracked devices and delivery activity. Asset data is Supported. Telemetry data is Supported. Writeback is Supported.",
